#: plugins/ocr/gocr/kookaocr-gocr.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (sometimes known as <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis>) is "
"an open source OCR engine, originally started by Joerg&nbsp;Schulenburg and "
"now with a team of active developers.<nl/><nl/>See <link url=\"http://jocr."
"sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> for more information on GOCR."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (batzuetan <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis> gisa ezaguna) "
"sorburu irekiko OCR motor bat da, jatorrian Joerg&nbsp;Schulenburg-ek hasia "
"eta orain garatzaile-talde aktibo bat duena.<nl/><nl/>Begiratu <link url="
"\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> GOCR-ren gaineko "
"informazio gehiago lortzeko."

#: plugins/ocr/ocrad/kookaocr-ocrad.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine by Antonio&nbsp;"
"Diaz, part of the GNU&nbsp;Project.<nl/><nl/>Images for OCR should be "
"scanned in black/white (lineart) mode. Best results are achieved if the "
"characters are at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise, as usual, "
"with very bold or very light or broken characters, or with merged character "
"groups.<nl/><nl/>See <link url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html"
"\">www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html</link> for more information on "
"OCRAD."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> Antonio&nbsp;Diaz-ek eginiko software irekiko OCR "
"motor bat da, GNU&nbsp;Proiektuaren zatia.<nl/><nl/>OCR-rako irudiak zuri/"
"beltz (lineart) moduan eskaneatu beharko lirateke. Emaitzarik onenak "
"karaktereak gutxienez 20&nbsp;pixeletako altuera dutenean lortzen dira. "
"Arazoak sor daitezke, ohi bezala, karaktere oso lodiekin edo oso argiekin "
"edo hautsiekin, edo batutako karaktere-multzoekin.<nl/><nl/>Begiratu <link "
"url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">www.gnu.org/software/"
"ocrad/ocrad.html</link> OCRAD-en gaineko informazio gehiago lortzeko."

#: plugins/ocr/tesseract/kookaocr-tesseract.json
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine, originally "
"developed at HP&nbsp;Labs and now sponsored by Google. It supports multiple "
"languages and scripts (including right-to-left text) and page layout "
"analysis.<nl/><nl/>The best results are achieved if scanned characters are "
"at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise with excessively skewed or "
"rotated images, or if dark borders are present.<nl/><nl/>See <link url="
"\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract\">github.com/tesseract-ocr/"
"tesseract</link> for more information on Tesseract."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> software askeko OCR motor bat da, jatorrian "
"HP&nbsp;Labs-ek garatua, egun Google-k babestua. Hainbat hizkuntza eta "
"idazkera (eskuinetik-ezkerrerako testua barne) eta orri antolaeraren "
"analisia onartzen ditu.<nl/><nl/>Emaitzarik onenak karaktereak gutxienez "
"20&nbsp;pixeletako altuera dutenean lortzen dira. Arazoak sor daitezke "
"gehiegi okertutako edo biratutako irudiekin, edo ertz ilunak badaude.<nl/"
"><nl/>Begiratu <link url=\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract"
"\">github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract</link> Tesseract-en gaineko informazio "
"gehiago lortzeko."

